description: This file is a build compilation command database (compile_commands.json) generated by CMake, listing compilation commands and source files for the plugin_appgateway component. It includes references to multiple source files related to the AppGateway plugin, such as AppGateway.cpp, AppGatewayImplementation.cpp, AppGatewayResponderImplementation.cpp, Resolver.cpp, and Module.cpp. The file itself does not contain actual source code content but rather metadata for the build system.
